  <trk>
    <name>Tour of Val d’Anniviers: Zinal–Grimentz (Stage 3)</name>
    <desc>The hike runs between two valleys: from the Val de Zinal you hike over a pass to the Lac de Moiry dam. From there, the descent begins through the pristine Val de Moiry to the destination of the hike in the picturesque village of Grimentz.</desc>
    <type>hikingTourTrail</type>
